title: CAP Barbell 100 LB Coated Hex Dumbbell Weight Set with Vertical Rack
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weights & Accessories › Dumbbells
description: The CAP 100 LB Coated Hex Dumbbell Weight Set with A-Frame Rack will add versatility, storage space, and reliability to your home gym. This set includes a pair of 5-pound, 10-pound, 15-pound and 20-pound rubber hex dumbbell weights and an A-frame rack to store them. The FIVE pairs of dumbbells can be easily stored and accessed using the reliable, durable, space-saving A-frame rack. The dumbbell heads are made from ASTM A48 Class 20 grey iron coated in 80 shore hardness rubber joined together by a solid 1018 cold rolled steel chromed handle, making them durable and reliable. Use dumbbells to target specific muscle groups or add resistance to your strength training routine or HIIT workout. This set allows you to start with light resistance and build your way up to heavier weights, allowing you to attain the fitness goals you’ve set.
features: SET INCLUDES – A pair of 5-pound, 10-pound, 15-pound and 20-pound rubber hex dumbbells with an A-frame dumbbell rack to store the weights. E-commerge packaging. This set ships in multiple boxes.

SPACE-SAVING DESIGN – The A-frame design of this rack maximizes floor space by storing dumbbells in an “A” shape, or vertical fashion. Easily access and store dumbbells. Rubber inserts prevent dumbbells and rack from scratches

DURABLE AND RELIABLE – Rack is made with steel and finished with durable black powder coat. Heads are made from ASTM A48 Class 20 grey iron and joined together by a 1018 cold rolled solid steel handle (sizes 15-120lb) with an extreme durable rubber coating.
VERSATILE – Dumbbells offer the ability to target specific muscle groups or perform a full body workout. Perfect for isolations, functional and HIIT workouts, and strength training routines
FEATURES – The original hex shaped heads prevent rolling. The medium depth knurling on the handle provides essential grip and security during use. Rubber coating is a durable and effective finish

features: Incredible Value: Our goal is to design a best home gym Olympic weightlifting bar at an affordable price. Here we made it! We enhanced the steel hardening process and surface treatment to make our bars stronger for repeated use. The high-grade steel used in this 700LBS bar was tested with 130,000 PSI tensile strength, adequate enough to handle all your demands. And it has a stunning look and great feel with overall black e-coat finish.

Superior Bearing and Bushing: For those who are tired of tightening the hex bolt end sleeves, LIONSCOOL Olympic Bar is for you. Our barbell has sleeves with the snap rings at both ends maintaining stability for a lifetime. aPlusContent.title: From the manufacturer
aPlusContent.rawText:
From the manufacturer

Barbell exercises are a form of resistance training. Resistance training is using your muscles to move resistance, usually weights. Examples of barbell resistance training are squats, bench press, barbell row, shoulder press, deadlifts and curls to name a few. Barbells allow you to move more weight than you could with a dumbbell because you have two hands on a fixed object. This makes it safer to learn new exercises.

These protein-rich treats offer a balanced combination of whey protein isolate, micellar casein, and fiber for sustained energy throughout your day.

title: Olympic Training Barbell (6FT) (15 Pound Weight) (300 LBS Capacity), Home Gym Fitness Equipment, Strength Training Workout Bar, Weight bar for Squats, Deadlift, Weightlifting, Bench Press
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weights & Accessories › Bars
description: Achieve a better build with the RAGE FITNESS Olympic Barbell that increases strength, stamina and cardiovascular endurance. These aluminum barbells are a perfect starter bar for teaching beginners the technique of Olympic lifting. They can also be used as a scaled-weight bar for full-throttle workouts. They are durable and spin freely. 300 lb. test.   WARRANTY INFO:  RAGE FITNESS EQUIPMENT (WITH THE EXCEPTION OF GRIPS) IS GUARANTEED FOR A PERIOD OF ONE YEAR FROM DATE OF INVOICE AGAINST FAULTY MANUFACTURING OR DEFECTS IN MATERIAL.    RAGE Fitness is built on sweat, passion, sacrifice and some of the strongest, most durable functional fitness equipment on the planet. RAGE (rāj) is all about explosive force, furious intensity and burning desire, and the products we offer prove it every day. We fuel the passion and intensity (a.k.a. the RAGE) for people who lift, jump, push, kick, run, climb, catch, twist, flip, resist, sweat and recover, and then do it all over again to push their athletic limits, reach their goals and improve their lives. The brand was born in 2008, but it didn't take long for RAGE to spread to gyms, boxes, garages and fitness clubs across the country and around the world.  RAGE erupted into retail in 2012 and since then has become the definitive, authentic and accessible functional fitness brand in sporting goods and fitness specialty.
features: 【 ERGONOMIC DESIGN 】: Our weight-lifting equipment features a comfortable grip area of 49 inches with 1.5mm deep diamond-knurled handles that provide a secure and non-slip grip during intense training sessions. The shaft and sleeves have a durable chrome finish that provides protection against corrosion and oxidation over time, as well as a stylish look in your professional gym or home gym.

【 OLYMPIC GRADE DURABILITY 】: For rigorous use and intense workout sessions, our 6ft strength training bar is constructed with high-quality aluminum that carries up to 300 LBS weight, designed to fit Olympic weight plates with a 2-inch hole, giving that perfect starting point for beginners to learn and master their technique.

【 HOME & GYM COMPANION 】: Whether setting up a home gym or training at a professional gym, our barbell is a perfect addition to your daily workout routine. It is compact and easy to store, making it convenient for personal and commercial use. Our exercise equipment allows you to perform a wide range of exercises such as squats, deadlifts, bench presses, overhead presses, hip thrusts, and more, targeting multiple muscle groups simultaneously, providing a full-body workout to build strength and muscle mass.

【 SEAMLESS ROTATION 】: Extra thick brass bushings and bearings in the sleeve allow for smooth rotation and reduced noise during movement, allowing the sleeve to rotate silently, reducing the amount of force produced off of the ground and thus reducing the risk of injury to the lifter and increasing the level of comfort in a lift for utmost safety.

【 SMOOTH & BALANCED PERFORMANCE 】: Rage Fitness barbell provides a smooth and balanced lifting experience. The weight distribution along the bar ensures stability and control during lifts, allowing you to focus on proper form and technique. Moreover, our training barbell securely holds the weight plates in place, preventing accidental slipping during exercises.

title: Synergee Games 15kg and 20kg Colored Ceramic Coated Barbells. Rated 1500lbs for Weightlifting and Powerlifting. Black, Red, Grey, Pink
inStockText: In Stock  Only 1 left in stock - order soon.
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weights & Accessories › Bars
description: Synergee barbells are made with world renowned steel! These barbells are made with a high tensile strength of 190,000 PSI. Made with the perfect amount of “whip” and “flex” for weightlifting, Synergee barbells still have the stiffness needed for heavy powerlifting, Olympic lifting, body building and crushing WODs. Each bar is tested for straightness and balance throughout the barbell. Comfort in your grip comes from the knurl. Our goal was to create a full and uniform pattern that is not too aggressive but still gives the maximum grip you need. The knurling on a barbell is ground onto the bar by a specialized machine. The pattern features two sets of diagonal lines, each set going in the opposite direction, so that they form thousands of tiny little diamonds. These diamonds keep your hands from slipping, ensuring your comfort throughout your workout. After testing multiple knurls, we settled on a standard knurl with dual knurl marks. The inner knurl mark is for powerlifting, while the outer is for Olympic weightlifting.
features: ★ SUPERIOR CONSTRUCTION ★ – Our Synergee Games Bar is built to handle your toughest workouts. From Olympic lifting to powerlifting to body building, its high-grade steel and Ceramic Coated composition, tensile strength rating of 190,000 PSI, 1500 lb weight capacity, 1.2 mm knurl, and 10 needle bearings can withstand it all.

★ FITTER, FASTER, STRONGER ★ - With a loadable sleeve length of 16.4 inches (20 kg) and 13 inches (15 KG), our barbell can carry heavy loads, helping you push out of your comfort zone and reach your potential. Created by athletes, for athletes, our Synergee Staff have witnessed members of our Synergee Community crush their PRs with the Games Bar, which is exactly why we created it.

★ CERAMIC COATED FINISH ★ – Our steel bar is finished with a CERAMIC COATED coating: you’ll look tired at the end of your workout, but this barbell won’t – even after years of use! Choose which color you want and get yourself a bar that suits your style as well as your workouts.
★ WHAT’S IN THE PACKAGE ★ – This bar is a Pink, 15 KG Barbell. It is 79.13 inches long, has 13 inch loadable sleeve lengths, and 25 MM in diameter. 10 bearings total (5 per sleeve).
★ NO SWEAT ★ – Leave the sweating and swearing for your training! Buying from Synergee means quick and caring customer service! Customer Satisfaction is our Number 1 Goal!

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Quality Fitness. Exceptional Durability. 
The Philosophy Gym Weightlifting Barbell Straight Bar is an excellent option for any lifter, fitness enthusiast, or bodybuilder. Having a standard barbell is an absolute must for your arsenal of gym equipment. Weightlifting from the comfort of home requires the right tools and equipment for successful training. 
The Philosophy Gym standard weightlifting barbell is offered in 5FT, 6FT, and 7FT lengths, enabling you plenty of options to customize your workouts. Perfect for home gyms, garage gyms, and ensuring you have the best equipment for working out anywhere, this weightlifting barbell is excellent for building muscle. Complete a total body workout targeting your upper and lower body by performing bench presses, squats, overhead presses, deadlifts, and many more. 
Our standard weightlifting bar features diamond knurled grips, and a chrome finished solid steel bar for added protection and longevity. Compatible with standard 1” plates, enabling you to add either 110 lbs., 160 lbs. or 200 lbs. maximum capacity, depending on bar length. It boasts a comfortable weight, along with a 1” sleeve diameter. If you’re seeking a durable, high-quality weightlifting barbell, you won’t find a better option than this! 
Philosophy Gym - Create Your Perfect Workout 
We at Philosophy Gym believe in providing premium quality commercial grade gym & fitness equipment that will inspire you to pursue your fitness goals. We offer the necessary equipment needed to help push you to your fullest potential, feel your best, and get you performing better, faster, and stronger - that’s our philosophy.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Quality Fitness. Exceptional Durability. 
The Philosophy Gym Weightlifting Barbell Straight Bar is an excellent option for any lifter, fitness enthusiast, or bodybuilder. Having a standard barbell is an absolute must for your arsenal of gym equipment. Weightlifting from the comfort of home requires the right tools and equipment for successful training. 
The Philosophy Gym standard weightlifting barbell is offered in 5FT, 6FT, and 7FT lengths, enabling you plenty of options to customize your workouts. Perfect for home gyms, garage gyms, and ensuring you have the best equipment for working out anywhere, this weightlifting barbell is excellent for building muscle. Complete a total body workout targeting your upper and lower body by performing bench presses, squats, overhead presses, deadlifts, and many more. 
Our standard weightlifting bar features diamond knurled grips, and a chrome finished solid steel bar for added protection and longevity. Compatible with standard 1” plates, enabling you to add either 110 lbs., 160 lbs. or 200 lbs. maximum capacity, depending on bar length. It boasts a comfortable weight, along with a 1” sleeve diameter. If you’re seeking a durable, high-quality weightlifting barbell, you won’t find a better option than this! 
Philosophy Gym - Create Your Perfect Workout 
We at Philosophy Gym believe in providing premium quality commercial grade gym & fitness equipment that will inspire you to pursue your fitness goals. We offer the necessary equipment needed to help push you to your fullest potential, feel your best, and get you performing better, faster, and stronger - that’s our philosophy.

title: CAP Barbell 100 LB Coated Hex Dumbbell Weight Set with Comfort Grip and with Vertical Rack
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weights & Accessories › Dumbbells
description: The CAP 100 LB Coated Hex Comfort Grip Dumbbell Weight Set with A-Frame Rack will add versatility, storage space, and reliability to your home gym. This set includes a pair of 5-pound, 10-pound, 15-pound and 20-pound rubber hex dumbbell weights and an A-frame rack to store them. The FIVE pairs of dumbbells can be easily stored and accessed using the reliable, durable, space-saving A-frame rack. The dumbbell heads are made from ASTM A48 Class 20 grey iron coated in 80 shore hardness rubber joined together by a solid 1018 cold rolled steel chromed handle, making them durable and reliable. Use dumbbells to target specific muscle groups or add resistance to your strength training routine or HIIT workout. This set allows you to start with light resistance and build your way up to heavier weights, allowing you to attain the fitness goals you’ve set.
features: SET INCLUDES – A pair of 5-pound, 10-pound, 15-pound and 20-pound rubber hex dumbbells with an A-frame dumbbell rack to store the weights. E-commerge packaging. This set ships in multiple boxes.

SPACE-SAVING DESIGN – The A-frame design of this rack maximizes floor space by storing dumbbells in an “A” shape, or vertical fashion. Easily access and store dumbbells. Rubber inserts prevent dumbbells and rack from scratches

DURABLE AND RELIABLE – Rack is made with steel and finished with durable black powder coat. Heads are made from ASTM A48 Class 20 grey iron and joined together by a 1018 cold rolled solid steel handle (sizes 15-120lb) with an extreme durable rubber coating.
VERSATILE – Dumbbells offer the ability to target specific muscle groups or perform a full body workout. Perfect for isolations, functional and HIIT workouts, and strength training routines
FEATURES – The original hex shaped heads prevent rolling. The medium depth knurling on the handle provides essential grip and security during use. Rubber coating is a durable and effective finish

title: WF Athletic Supply 7 ft 2-inch Olympic Weighted Solid Steel Bar Barbell, for Weightlifting/Bench Press/Deadlift and Power Lifting Strength Training, with Rotating Sleeve, Home Gym
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weights & Accessories › Bars
description: WF Athletic Supply 7 ft 2-inch Olympic Weighted Solid Steel Bar Barbell, for Weightlifting/Bench Press/Deadlift and Power Lifting Strength Training, with Rotating Sleeve, Home Gym
features: Specs - Measures 2185 millimeter in length; Shaft length of 51.75”; Loadable sleeve length of 15.3”; Handgrip diameter of 30 millimeter; 63,800 PSI tensile strength steel; Weighs 35 lbs; Center knurl 4.75”; Side knurling 10.75”

Heavy-Duty Construction - The barbell is made from solid cold rolled steel with a black finish to protect the barbell bar from corrosion and stand the test of time. The 35 lb Olympic bar offers performance for powerlifting routines. Accommodates Olympic weight plates with a 2-inch center hole.

500LB Capacity - Our Olympic lifting barbell can hold 500 lbs weight capacity with a 63,800 PSI tensile strength. Recommended for home-use free weight exercises. The loadable sleeve length is 15.3 inches, providing plenty of room to load your Olympic weights.

Knurling - The knurled 30 mm handgrip diameter ensures a tight, non-slip grip when lifting. Medium depth knurling and center knurling for a secure grip. A Diamond Knurl pattern provides an excellent gripping surface without the sharpness of other grips, has a moderate whip, increases friction, and improves the grip experience.
Rotating Sleeves - Bushings provide a comprehensive smooth spin which reduces stress on your wrists and elbows. Preventing the bar from warping and providing a more secure grip.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
WF Athletic Supply is committed to helping athletes, at all levels, succeed in sports of their choice by providing the best strength, conditioning, and speed, and agility equipment. Our goals are the same as those of our athletes: to improve overall athleticism, to develop discipline, and to achieve success with a well-trained mind and body. 
Barbell Features 
Rotating Sleeves 
- Bushings provide a comprehensive smooth spin which reduces stress on your wrists and elbows. Preventing the bar from warping and providing a more secure grip. 
500 LB Capacity 
- The barbell is made from solid cold rolled steel with a Black finish to protect the barbell bar from corrosion and stand the test of time. 
Knurling 
- A Diamond Knurl pattern provides an excellent gripping surface without the sharpness of other grips, has a moderate whip, increases friction, and improves the grip experience. 
Barbell Specifications 

Specifications 
Overall Weight: 35 lbs 
Weight Capacity: 500 lbs 
Loadable Sleeve Length: 15.3 inches for each side 
Shaft Length: 51.75 inches 
Overall Length: 86 inches (7 feet) 
7 ft 2-inch Olympic 35 LB Black Solid Steel Bar Barbell 
Meticulously designed to meet your highest expectations 
Constructed with utmost care using premium-grade materials, it stands as a testament to its enduring quality. The bar's medium-depth diamond knurling grip pattern offers a secure and comfortable hold, empowering you to tackle your workouts with confidence. 
Experience the epitome of durability, grip, and smoothness with our remarkable Olympic barbell bar. 
An ideal choice for cross-fit workouts, weightlifting, overhead presses, deadlifts, bench presses, and more. 
Color Options: Black Zinc / Chrome 
Knurling Style: Diamond 
Diameter of Sleeve: 2 inches 
Grip Size: 30 mm 
Multi-functional Training 
This versatile barbell excels in diverse workouts, accommodating Olympic lifting, powerlifting, and accessory exercises. It offers impressive weight capacity, excellent whip, and compatibility with Olympic weight plates. It's the ideal bar for all your fitness challenges. An ideal choice for cross-fit workouts, weightlifting, overhead presses, deadlifts, bench presses, and more.

title: CAP Barbell 100 lb Neoprene Hex Dumbbell Weight Set with Vertical A-Frame Rack - Black
inStockText: Only 1 left in stock - order soon.
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weights & Accessories › Dumbbells
description: CAP Barbell 60 LB Neoprene Hex Dumbbell Weight Set with Black Vertical A-Frame Rack will add versatility, storage space, and reliability to your home gym. This set includes a pair of 5-pound, 8-pound, 10-pound, 12-pound and 15-pound of Neoprene Hex Dumbbells and an Vertical A-Frame rack to store them. The 5 pairs of dumbbells can be easily stored and accessed using the reliable, durable, space-saving Vertical A-Frame rack. The construction consists Iron core made from ASTM A48 Grade 20 grey iron then precision dipped in 3mm of neoprene for safety and comfort. Use dumbbells to target specific muscle groups or add resistance to your strength training routine or HIIT workout. This set allows you to start with light resistance and build your way up to heavier weights, allowing you to attain the fitness goals you’ve set.
features: SET INCLUDES – A pair of 5-pound, 8-pound, 10-pound, 12-pound, and 15-pound black neoprene coated dumbbells with a black A-frame dumbbell rack to store the weights. E-commerce packaging. This set ships in multiple boxes.

SPACE-SAVING DESIGN – The A-frame design of this rack maximizes floor space by storing dumbbells in an “A” shape, or vertical fashion. Easily access and store dumbbells. Rubber inserts prevent dumbbells and rack from scratches

DURABLE AND RELIABLE – Rack is made with steel and finished with durable black powder coat. Iron core made from ASTM A48 Grade 20 grey iron then precision dipped in 3mm of neoprene for safety and comfort.
VERSATILE – Dumbbells offer the ability to target specific muscle groups or perform a full body workout. Perfect for isolations, functional and HIIT workouts, and strength training routines
FEATURES – The original hex shaped heads prevent rolling. The medium depth knurling on the handle provides essential grip and security during use. Rubber coating is a durable and effective finish

aPlusContent.rawText:
From the manufacturer
Multi-Box Shipping: Optimized for Safety and Product Integrity with CAP Barbell 
When you purchase CAP Barbell products, you can trust that our shipping methods are designed to enhance safety and protect product integrity. We often ship weight products in multiple boxes to ensure that your order arrives in perfect condition. By dividing heavy or bulky items into several manageable packages, we prevent damage during transit and reduce the risk of injury for delivery personnel, who can handle lighter boxes more easily. This approach also allows for better distribution of weight, resulting in faster delivery times. CAP Barbell is committed to providing you with the highest quality products, delivered safely and efficiently. 
For any questions or concerns - Please reach out to CAP Barbell.

features: A Great Starter Set: This set includes 2 olympic dumbbell bars and 2 spring collars. The bar is 16" in length with a 25mm handgrip diameter. Each bar weighs 8.3 LB unloaded, but reaches the weight of 8.3 LB when combined with 2 pair of spring collars

For Olympic Plates: These dumbbell handles are compatible with olympic weights with 2" holes. Get these bars and utilize your weights to make your own adjustable dumbbells. No need to buy a complete set of traditional DBs. Save your money and storage space
Rotating Sleeve: The rotating sleeves of dumbbell bars allow weight plates to rotate when going heavier, which relieve stress during curling and other dynamic movements

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Space Efficient, Easy to Use 
If you have bought a bulk of olympic plates for your home gym, you should also get this pair of bars without hesitation. These bars are loadable and compatible with any standard-size Olympic plates, which enables you to take advantage of your weights and get a set of adjustable dumbbells insantly. No need to invest in a complete set of traditional dumbbells. Save your storage space and money. 
Adjustable dumbbells are the obvious choice allowing you to maximize the variety of workouts you can perform. Based on the weights plates you have, You can go from bench press to bicep curls at different weight levels. 
This makes the loadable dumbbell well suited for a larger gym—where multiple athletes can quickly customize the dumbbell to their own needs—or a small home gym, as it can eliminate the need for storing a full set of traditional dumbbells.

Has this dumbbell got various weight options or is it just available in one fixed weight or a few set combinations? 
This 44-pound dumbbell set includes 4* (1.65 + 2.75 + 5.51)-pound weight plates, enabling free adjustment from 3.3 to 44 pounds for desired combinations to suit various workout intensities and fitness goals. 
How's the quality of the coating on the dumbbell? Will it peel or fade easily during use? 
DICAO dumbbells feature a top-notch coating, crafted to endure regular workouts. It's firmly bonded and won't peel or fade easily with proper use. Of course, avoid harsh chemicals and rough handling to keep it in prime condition. 
Give the floor area that the dumbbells take up so as to work out whether they'll fit in the storage space or not.

aPlusContent.title: From the manufacturer
aPlusContent.rawText:
From the manufacturer
Benefits of the EZ Bar for Upper Body Workouts 
Ergonomic Design for Comfort: The EZ bar’s distinctive curved shape minimizes wrist strain by providing a more natural grip. This ergonomic design enhances comfort during exercises and lowers the risk of injury, especially during repetitive movements.
Improved Muscle Engagement: The EZ bar excels in exercises like bicep curls and tricep extensions, allowing for better muscle targeting. Its design supports a fuller range of motion, optimizing muscle activation and promoting more effective growth.
Versatility for All Fitness Levels: Whether you're a beginner or an experienced lifter, the EZ bar is highly adaptable. It can be integrated into various upper body exercises, boosting overall strength and muscle development while offering a safer and more controlled workout experience.
4 FT EZ Bar 
Features: The EZ curl bar has bends in the bar, reducing strain on the wrists, making it ideal for curls (like bicep exercises) and tricep extensions.
Ideal for: Beginners or those focusing on arm exercises, especially those who find holding a straight barbell uncomfortable for long periods.
Uses: Bicep curls, tricep extensions, shoulder curls, etc.
5 FT Strength Training Bar 
Features: Shorter than Olympic bars, a 5ft bar is more maneuverable in limited spaces and lighter than an Olympic bar.
Ideal for: Beginners or those with limited space. It’s also suitable for women or smaller men who want to start with lighter weight training.
Uses: Basic strength exercises like squats, bench presses, and rows.
6 FT Strength Training Bar 
Features: Slightly longer than the 5ft bar, it provides more stability and can hold more weight.
Ideal for: Intermediate lifters with some training experience, or those with limited space but wanting to increase the weight they can lift.
Uses: Full-body strength exercises, including squats, bench presses, and deadlifts.
7 FT Olympic Bar 
Features: This is the standard competition bar, designed for heavy load-bearing and capable of supporting significant weight. It's heavier than other bars and fits standard Olympic weight plates.
Ideal for: Advanced lifters, those focused on powerlifting or Olympic lifting, or those with enough space for such equipment.
Uses: Heavy squats, bench presses, deadlifts, and overhead presses for high-intensity strength training.
Benefits of the Olympic Barbell for Strength Training 
Durable and Versatile: Built for heavy lifting, the Olympic barbell’s sturdy design withstands intense training, making it perfect for a wide range of exercises such as squats, deadlifts, and bench presses. Its versatility allows for both power and strength training.
Maximized Muscle Engagement: The Olympic barbell excels in compound movements that activate multiple muscle groups simultaneously. It enhances overall strength, focusing on key areas like the lower body, posterior chain, and upper body, driving balanced muscle development.
Adaptable for All Fitness Levels: Whether you're a beginner or an experienced lifter, the Olympic barbell is a foundational tool for progressive strength gains. Its ability to accommodate varying loads makes it essential for achieving muscle growth and fitness goals at any stage of training.

modules.title: Benefits of the EZ Bar for Upper Body Workouts
modules.text:
Ergonomic Design for Comfort: The EZ bar’s distinctive curved shape minimizes wrist strain by providing a more natural grip. This ergonomic design enhances comfort during exercises and lowers the risk of injury, especially during repetitive movements.
Improved Muscle Engagement: The EZ bar excels in exercises like bicep curls and tricep extensions, allowing for better muscle targeting. Its design supports a fuller range of motion, optimizing muscle activation and promoting more effective growth.
Versatility for All Fitness Levels: Whether you're a beginner or an experienced lifter, the EZ bar is highly adaptable. It can be integrated into various upper body exercises, boosting overall strength and muscle development while offering a safer and more controlled workout experience.

items.title: 4 FT EZ Bar
items.text:
Features: The EZ curl bar has bends in the bar, reducing strain on the wrists, making it ideal for curls (like bicep exercises) and tricep extensions.
Ideal for: Beginners or those focusing on arm exercises, especially those who find holding a straight barbell uncomfortable for long periods.
Uses: Bicep curls, tricep extensions, shoulder curls, etc.

items.title: 5 FT Strength Training Bar
items.text:
Features: Shorter than Olympic bars, a 5ft bar is more maneuverable in limited spaces and lighter than an Olympic bar.
Ideal for: Beginners or those with limited space. It’s also suitable for women or smaller men who want to start with lighter weight training.
Uses: Basic strength exercises like squats, bench presses, and rows.

items.title: 6 FT Strength Training Bar
items.text:
Features: Slightly longer than the 5ft bar, it provides more stability and can hold more weight.
Ideal for: Intermediate lifters with some training experience, or those with limited space but wanting to increase the weight they can lift.
Uses: Full-body strength exercises, including squats, bench presses, and deadlifts.

items.title: 7 FT Olympic Bar
items.text:
Features: This is the standard competition bar, designed for heavy load-bearing and capable of supporting significant weight. It's heavier than other bars and fits standard Olympic weight plates.
Ideal for: Advanced lifters, those focused on powerlifting or Olympic lifting, or those with enough space for such equipment.
Uses: Heavy squats, bench presses, deadlifts, and overhead presses for high-intensity strength training.

modules.title: Benefits of the Olympic Barbell for Strength Training
modules.text:
Durable and Versatile: Built for heavy lifting, the Olympic barbell’s sturdy design withstands intense training, making it perfect for a wide range of exercises such as squats, deadlifts, and bench presses. Its versatility allows for both power and strength training.
Maximized Muscle Engagement: The Olympic barbell excels in compound movements that activate multiple muscle groups simultaneously. It enhances overall strength, focusing on key areas like the lower body, posterior chain, and upper body, driving balanced muscle development.
Adaptable for All Fitness Levels: Whether you're a beginner or an experienced lifter, the Olympic barbell is a foundational tool for progressive strength gains. Its ability to accommodate varying loads makes it essential for achieving muscle growth and fitness goals at any stage of training.

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Needle bearing only really important in weightlifting movements, where a lot of rotational momentum is forced into the barbell (and therefore plates) because of the movement patterns. 
If the barbell doesn't spin, the torque can be areal problem, causing injury or lifter off balance. 
PAPABABE Olympic barbell: Ideal Equipment for Exercise 
PAPABABE Olympic barbells are made from high quality materials and treated with an oxidation resistant zinc plating to provide a long lasting barbell. Made to fit weight plates with 2" center holes, they are also known as Olympic weights. 
The barbell is the simplest looking piece of equipment in the gym, but it’s one of the most complex equipment to learn how to use. When a beginning trainer uses a barbell for the first time, the body’s response is mainly mental. Learning how to move a barbell teaches our minds how to use all of our muscles together to move an object efficiently. Olympic barbell moves require balance and coordination, unlike machines, resulting in better performance during fitness competitions. 
We suggest adding PAPABABE weight plates and power cage to get more fit! 
Black Zinc and Diamond Knurling 
The black part of the surface is treated with zinc plating, Diamond knurled handle design for easy controlled lifting to target desired muscle groups while reducing risk of injury. 
Bearings, not Bushing 
Using bearings for smooth sleeve rotation, designed to reduce pressure on wrists and forearms, and match the catching needs of the snatch and clean & jerk. 
Center Knurl 
The center knurl will help keep the bar in place on your back during back squats and on your chest for front squats.

aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Needle bearing only really important in weightlifting movements, where a lot of rotational momentum is forced into the barbell (and therefore plates) because of the movement patterns. 
If the barbell doesn't spin, the torque can be areal problem, causing injury or lifter off balance. 
PAPABABE Olympic barbell: Ideal Equipment for Exercise 
PAPABABE Olympic barbells are made from high quality materials and treated with an oxidation resistant zinc plating to provide a long lasting barbell. Made to fit weight plates with 2" center holes, they are also known as Olympic weights. 
The barbell is the simplest looking piece of equipment in the gym, but it’s one of the most complex equipment to learn how to use. When a beginning trainer uses a barbell for the first time, the body’s response is mainly mental. Learning how to move a barbell teaches our minds how to use all of our muscles together to move an object efficiently. Olympic barbell moves require balance and coordination, unlike machines, resulting in better performance during fitness competitions. 
We suggest adding PAPABABE weight plates and power cage to get more fit! 
Black Zinc and Diamond Knurling 
The black part of the surface is treated with zinc plating, Diamond knurled handle design for easy controlled lifting to target desired muscle groups while reducing risk of injury. 
Bearings, not Bushing 
Using bearings for smooth sleeve rotation, designed to reduce pressure on wrists and forearms, and match the catching needs of the snatch and clean & jerk. 
Center Knurl 
The center knurl will help keep the bar in place on your back during back squats and on your chest for front squats.

aPlusContent.rawText:
From the manufacturer
CAP Barbell Olympic 2-Inch Plate Rack 
RK-2A 
Keep your weight plates off the floor and right where you need them with the CAP Barbell 2 inch Plate Rack. Made for either home or commercial use, this rack offers ample storage for 2-inch Olympic plates, with 7 posts to store weights safely. Constructed of heavy-gauge steel and powder coated in black, this storage rack is durable and will last for years to come. 
Assembled Dimensions 
The assembled dimensions measure 22" Length x 19" Wide x 37" Height. 
Recommended Weight Capacity 
The recommended weight capacity for this rack is 500-pounds. 
Features 
7 Posts to Store Olympic Weights 
Steel Construction for Stability 
Black Powder Coat Finish for Durability 
Rubber Base to Protect Floors 
Heavy Duty and Reliable 
The rubber feet on the bottom of this Olympic Plate Storage Rack will prevent your floor from getting scratched or damaged, while the 7 posts with 2-inch diameter are securely welded to the metal frame to provide a safe place to store your Olympic weights. The sleek black powder coat finish adds a touch of shine to your gym and protects the rack from rusting.

breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weights & Accessories › Dumbbells
features: SET INCLUDES – A pair of 5-pound, 10-pound, 15-pound, 20-pound, and 25-pound rubber hex dumbbells with a Two Tier white dumbbell rack to store the weights. E-commerce packaging. This set ships in multiple boxes.
SPACE-SAVING DESIGN – The Two Tier design of this rack maximizes floor space. Easily access and store dumbbells. Rubber inserts prevent dumbbells and rack from scratches

DURABLE AND RELIABLE – Rack is made with steel and finished with durable black powder coat. Heads are made from ASTM A48 Class 20 grey iron and joined together by a 1018 cold rolled solid steel handle (sizes 15-120lb) with an extreme durable rubber coating.
VERSATILE – Dumbbells offer the ability to target specific muscle groups or perform a full body workout. Perfect for isolations, functional and HIIT workouts, and strength training routines
FEATURES – The original hex shaped heads prevent rolling. The medium depth knurling on the handle provides essential grip and security during use. Rubber coating is a durable and effective finish

title: Sportneer Barbell Pad Set: 10Pcs Squat Pad for Hip Thrusts, Lunges, Leg Day, Standard Olympic Bars with 2 Ankle Straps, 2 Lifting Straps, 3 Resistance Bands, Barbell Pad, Workout Poster and Carry Bag
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Exercise Machine Parts & Accessories › Exercise Machine Attachments
features: EXCLUSIVE BARBELL PAD SET: Hands up to anyone who feels sick when spotting the stinky public fitness items! Then why not have our woman-exclusive barbell pad set? What makes the Sportneer 10PCS gym essentials set really shine is that it boasts 1 barbell squat pad, 2 gym ankle straps, 2 weightlifting straps, 3 strength resistance bands, 1 carry bag, and 1 training guide. Bonus time -- the included 21-day workout log helps track your progress and hit your goals!

ULTIMATE COMFORT HIP SQUAT PAD: Featuring 30x higher-density rubber foam, the Sportneer barbell pad ensures a pain-free workout by alleviating any discomfort in your neck, back, and vertebrae area during hip thrusts or squats. Also, the ergonomic pad is designed to be versatile. It comes with 4 buckle straps, making it suitable for a range of barbell bars, including standard bars, Olympic bars, Smith machines, and most other barbell bars, and the bearing capacity can reach about 400kg.

STRONG & STABILITY ANKLE STRAPS: We spared no effort in finding the ultimate comfort gym ankle cuffs for working out without compromising on the durability and longevity that our reinforced nylon exterior and extra-large stainless steel D-rings provide. High-quality Ankle Cable Attachments for Gym help you achieve your fitness goals and aid in strengthening and sculpting your lower body muscle into the physique you desire.

HIGH-END EXERCISE BANDS: Our gym accessories set also comes in 3 heavy-duty loop resistance bands. Made of premium-quality natural latex material, the resistance bands offer a smooth and bright appearance and provide superior durability. They are not easy to crack. Non-toxic and skin-friendly to the human body. These workout bands can be integrated with other gym equipment. Or use them for general exercise, stretching, or strength training.

BUILT TO LAST GYM LIFTING WRIST WRAPS: “SHAPE YOUR NICE BOOTY"—Our Sportneer weight lifting straps with the inspiring slogan printed on the straps, are designed to strengthen your grips so that you can lift heavier weights with NO fear of slipping. Also, our lifting straps are made of heavy-duty polypropylene, double walking lines increase durability, and neoprene padding cushions wrists, which will definitely give you new confidence to go for PR attempts.

aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Solid Steel Material 
The barbell bar is made exclusively from solid steel and hard chrome coating. The chrome coating can enhance the hardness and strength of the barbell surface and protect the barbell from rust and wear. 
Knurled Grip 
This weight bar adopts the knurled handles for improving grip. These knurls not only increase friction, but also have anti-slip properties. Besides, they can increase the safety of your exercises and ensure a comfortable, consistent feel during sets. 
Workout & Home Gym 
The superior design of this bar allows for a wide variety of workouts such as bench presses, bicep curling, piggybacking, overhead pressure or lunge. 
with 2 Spring Collar 
One of the most important aspects of lifting is the ability to achieve a strong, tight, controlled and well-placed grip. 
Wide Compatibility 
This barbell bar adopts exquisite design and is suitable for all weight plates with 2in aperture, which can meet your various strength training. 
360 ° Rotating Sleeves 
The sleeves are designed with bushings for a smooth spin. This prevents the bar from warping and reduces pressure on the wrists and forearms

title: Sunny Health & Fitness Strength Training Olympic Hex Bar Barbell, High Load Capacity, Swivel Handles, Safety Clips, Knurled Handles for Deadlifts, Shoulder Presses, Shrugs, Back Rows, Weightlifting
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weights & Accessories › Bars
features: HIGH LOAD CAPACITY: Stack on weights for a total max capacity of 400 LB for an intense lifting workout. Perform deadlifts, bent over rows, presses, squats, carry’s, lifts and much more!

SWIVEL HANDLES: Unique swivel handles enhance comfort and grip, allowing you to lift the way you prefer. Whether using a vertical or horizontal grip, this Olympic hex barbell ensures a smooth experience.
SAFETY CLIPS: Missing weight clamps? No problem. The included safety clips assures that your weight plates are stable and secure so you can stay focus on those deadlifts and squats instead.

KNURLED PATTERNED GRIP: Diamond knurled handles are designed for comfort, so your hands and palm won’t be scratched and/or cut while lifting heavier weights. Knurling is optimal for supplementing your own grip strength and helping correct hand placement.
LONG SLEEVES: Measuring at over 11 inches long, the sleeves provide adequate length for fitting multiple weight plates with different weight combinations.

ENVIRONMENT FRIENDLY: Sunny is not only committed to the improvement and development of a healthy lifestyle of fitness enthusiast but also to our environment. This hex trap weight barbell is packaged with the latest in resource-efficient, molded fiber and biodegradable materials while maintaining its protective structural integrity. Fully ISTA-6 certified to meet the most stringent durability standards.

aPlusContent.title: From the manufacturer
aPlusContent.rawText:
From the manufacturer
Multigrip Barbell 
Get A Grip On That Next Level. 
Benefits 
Provides Extra Versatility 
Our Swiss bar has 6 different grips (including 1 set of angled and 2 sets of neutral grips) to add variety to your barbell workouts. Additionally, it is designed to fit all Olympic weight plates, suitable for athletic strength and recovery training. 
Reduces Injury Risks 
The ergonomically positioned grips help prevent injuries usually caused by working with a regular barbell. Simply switch up grip positions until you find one that’s more suitable. The bar also comes with 2 extra barbell collars for increased safety. 
Improves Lifting Performance 
You can train specific muscle groups as well as incorporating a wide variation of isolation exercises with our hybrid bar, which can result in fresh gains and help overcome plateau. 
Features 
Different Handle Grips 
Equipped with 6 different knurled handle grips including neutral and angled grips, this hybrid bar offers versatility to your barbell workouts as well as reducing stress on your shoulders and wrists. 
Durable Steel Construction 
Made of heavy duty steel material with anti-rust black powder coating for maximum durability. Additionally, the bar’s 400lbs weight capacity adds strong support and sustained stability. 
Barbell Collars Included 
Comes with 2 additional T-Screw barbell collars to be used to keep your weight plates in place, helping to balance the barbell when lifting. 
Product Specifications 
Color: Black
Size: 82.2 x 7.5 x 2.8 inches
Weight: 22 lbs
Material: Steel

Benefits

How to convert dumbbells to barbells? 
1. Turn knob cover; 2. Open the fixture; 3. Place the dumbbells in the jig; 4. Tighten the knob cover after pressing the fixture. 
What are the size requirements for dumbbell handles? 
Handle length needs to be at least 4.5" long. Most dumbbell handles are approximately 6" long, The dumbbell handle's diameter cannot exceed 1.5" at its thickest point. 
How much weight can this weight bar hold? 
Load capacity up to 280 lbs. Thickened metal rod edges and nylon clips greatly increase weight capacity. 
Is it suitable to help me with a full body workout? 
The barbell bar is a versatile piece of fitness equipment that can help you with weight lifting and strength training such as bench presses, deep squats, deadlifts, hip thrusts, curls, bicep curls, and more. 
What are its best features? 
This dumbbell converter offers versatility and easy storage. You can use dumbbells that you already have instead of having to buy a bunch of barbell plates and barbells.

title: POWER GUIDANCE Olympic Barbell Solid Bar, 7ft Strength Training Bar for Weightlifting, Home Fitness, 1600-Pound Capacity
inStockText: Only 11 left in stock - order soon.
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weights & Accessories › Bars
features: Sturdy：Made of A3 solid steel, the Olympic Barbell has an overall weight of 45 lbs, is capable of holding up to 1600 lbs of weight plate and absorbs heavy loads, and has a tensile strength of 190,000 psi for maximum safety and support during intense lifts.

Medium Knurling & Durable Coating：Weight barbell with medium depth knurling, it has enough knurling for your heavy lifting but no shark tooth knurling that will tear your hands for higher rep workouts. The black chrome finish creates a stunning look and durability.

Quiet & Comfortable：Each swivel sleeve has 4 needle bearings and 1 brass bushing, with a total of 8 needle bearings in the rod, which reduces noise during motion and ensures quiet, smooth and consistent rotation of the sleeve for improved comfort and safety.

Strength Training Companion：Powerlifting bar knurled detail is precise enough to grip, exercise in a more standard posture, stimulate the biceps and triceps more deeply, perfect for deadlifts, bench presses, barbell curls. Makes strength training a breeze.

Wide range of application：7" Olympic bar can meet all your training needs, suitable for athletes of professional size and level, and can be used at home to build muscle and relieve stress. A great addition to your weight room and a great choice for a home gym.

title: Yes4All Viking Press Attachment – Great Landmine Exercise Equipment for 2-Inch Olympic Barbell
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Exercise Machine Parts & Accessories › Exercise Machine Attachments
description: Add more exercises to your strengthening regime with this simple but effective Viking Press Landmine Handle Attachment. Our Landmine Attachment allows for a range of rotational as well as compound exercises. HEAVY-DUTY STEEL LANDMINE ATTACHMENT FOR BARBELL Yes4All Viking Press Landmine Handle Attachment is designed with 7” long barbell tube to fit 2” Olympic barbell. The landmine attachment is made of heavy-gauge steel with a protective black paint coating finish to prevent chipping, scratching & fading. DESIGNED FOR DURABILITY AND VERSATILITY Yes4All Viking Press Landmine Handle Attachment comes with 3 grip positions to add versatility to your landmine training while also reducing stress and strain on your wrists and shoulders. Our Viking Press Landmine Handle Attachment is excellent for total body core workouts, including traps, biceps, back, shoulders, abs, and hamstrings. Great for Landmine Deadlift, Kickstand Romanian Deadlift, Squat, Overhead Squat, Reverse Lunge, Clean and Press, Split Jerk, Bent Over Row, and more. PRODUCT SPECIFICATIONS: Handle’s dimensions: 5” x 1. 7” & 5. 5 x 1. 7” (LxDia) Tube’s dimensions: 7” x 2. 047” (LxDia) Material: Steel with black paint finish Safety knob, bolts, and plastic insert included for easy installation 1-year & 30-day return.
features: SOLID STEEL CONSTRUCTION: Constructed of heavy gauge steel and covered with a black paint coating finish, Yes4All Viking Landmine Handle Attachment stands for years without corrosion or breaking apart during your heavy workouts

3 ERGONOMIC GRIP POSITIONS: The multi grip handle attachment with 1 7/8 inches diameter is equipped with 3 different grip positions to increase versatility and target specific muscle groups during your landmine workout

FIT 2 INCHES OLYMPIC BARBELL: Designed with 7 inches long tube, Yes4All Landmine Attachment is compatible with 2 inches Olympic barbell; Simply slide your barbell over the Handle and then tighten the knob for a secure workout

15 INCHES SPACE BETWEEN HANDLES: Unlike other products with a narrow gap between handles, our Viking Press Landmine Handle Attachment is designed with 15 inches gap to create more space for your head not to get smacked during Incline Presses
SATISFACTION GUARANTEED: Place your order and enjoy a 30-day Return policy and 1-year Warranty. Please note that barbells, weight plates, and landmine insert/T-bar row insert are NOT included.

description: UKEEP Adjustable Dumbbells Set, 20/30/40/55/60/70/80/90lbs Free Weight Set with Connector, 2 or 3 in 1 Dumbbells Set Used as Barbell, Kettlebells, Fitness Exercises for Home Gym Suitable Men/Women
features: 2-in-1 Multifunctional Dumbbell Set: The UKEEP Adjustable Dumbbell Set combines dumbbells and barbells into one versatile package. With adjustable weights ranging from 20/30/40/60/80lbs, it's perfect for various fitness exercises, including bench presses and squats. Ideal for both home gyms and professional use.

Sturdy and No Odor: The interior of this free weight dumbbell set is a mix of iron, clay and sand The exterior is made of high quality polyethylene material that is durable and odorless. This sturdy construction ensures longevity and prevents wear and tear on the floor, making it a reliable choice for your workouts.

Cutout Grippable Design: Unlike traditional round weight plates, our dumbbell plates are cut out for easy one-handed gripping and superior stability, ensuring a safer workout. This unique design enhances your control during your workout, making it perfect for a variety of exercises.

Quick and Easy Adjustments: This adjustable dumbbell set allows for quick and easy weight changes, with a single dumbbell's adjustable weight range from 4lbs to 10lbs. The detachable design makes weight adjustments simple, ensuring you can switch between different exercises seamlessly, from light workouts to intense training sessions.

Comfortable and Safe Design: The connecting rod of the barbell weight set is crafted from 5mm thick steel and 20mm thick high-quality foam. Its curved design comfortably fits the neck, offering non-slip and sweat-absorbing properties to ensure a safe and comfortable workout experience.

Non-Slip Dumbbell Bars: The dumbbell bars are made from ABS environmentally friendly material and feature a non-slip texture, enhancing hand grip and control during workouts. This design helps you manage the dumbbells better, improving your exercise efficiency and safety.

High-Quality Safety Double Nuts: This adjustable dumbbell set includes four safety double nuts. The thickened threads on the nuts effectively keep the weight plates secure, double nuts design preventing movement or shaking during workouts. This ensures your safety and provides a stable exercise experience.

title: ProsourceFit Olympic Barbell Spring Clip Collar 2-inch Pair with Easy-Grip Handles for Weightlifting,Powerlifting and Strength Training
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weights & Accessories › Collars
description: Ensure your safety when you’re lifting weights, whether it’s explosive workouts, heavy powerlifting, or general strength training. A sliding weight or bumper plate can not only cause you to lose balance, but can be a serious safety hazard. Prevent injuries and stay focused on your perfect form by using ProsourceFit Olympic Spring Clip Collars. The sturdy chromed steel collars provide ample tension to secure plates on any standard 2-inch barbell. Smooth plastic handles make them easy to grip and slip on and off as you increase weight, ideal when your hands are sweaty from an intense training session! The simple design is easy to use and provides a secure fit every time. At only 7.8 oz per clip, you’ll only add a miniscule amount to your bar, and they’re compact enough you can keep a pair in your gym bag for those times when all of the other clips at the gym are being used. They’re also ideal for home gyms. Get a few pairs so you don’t have to switch them around as often – one set for the bench, and one for the squat rack. These are a necessary piece of equipment for serious athletes, ideal for squats, deadlifts, cleans, bench presses, snatches, and more. You can also feel secure in your purchase with a limited lifetime warranty on these clips and all ProsourceFit fitness products.
features: COMFORT GRIP HANDLES – Smooth plastic handles make it easy to squeeze the collar and put it in place, even with sweaty hands
SAFER LIFTS – Clips hold weight plates in place to prevent them from sliding off of the barbell during heavy or explosive lifts
SECURE GRIP – Clamps tightly to the barbell and maintains tension so you don’t have to worry about it moving around
FITS STANDARD 2” BAR – Sturdy chrome-plated steel springs are sized to perfectly fit onto typical 2” Olympic barbell sleeves
SIMPLE TO USE – Just squeeze & slip on! These simple, reliable spring clips (sold in pairs) are a classic tool and a must-have for any weight lifter

aPlusContent.title: From the manufacturer
aPlusContent.rawText:
From the manufacturer

ProsourceFIT makes high quality products for strength and resistance training, performance, muscle recovery, yoga and Pilates. Our fitness equipment is made with commercial gym quality at prices that also makes them ideal for home workouts. We exist to inspire active, healthy lifestyles with products that make fitness attainable and enjoyable for everyone. Our extensive line of equipment is perfect for home workouts, personal trainers, strength training, yoga studios, and gyms of all types. 
Get more secure weight lifting sessions no matter how heavy you are pushing with ProsourceFit Olympic Spring Clip Collars. Made of durable steel and designed with plastic handles, the quick release clips are easy to grip even when your hands get sweaty. Release with ease on and off standard 2" barbells while ensuring plates don’t move or slide off so you can focus on your training even during overhead presses and heavy squats. 
Sold in a set of 2 
Lightweight & secure hold 
Made of durable chrome steel 
Plastic handles for non-slip grip 
Comfort Grip 
Eliminate extra stress from workouts with plastic grips that make your weight training easier. High quality plastic covered spring lock collars make it easy to use with one hand, allowing you to quickly transition from exercises seamlessly. 
Quick Release Design 
No more fumbling around! Simply squeeze to slip on or off standard 2" barbells hassle free for efficient transitions between exercises during your workouts! 
Compact & Lightweight 
Although sturdy, these spring clips weigh only 8.7oz each. It won't affect your workout or create extra bulk in your gym bag, so now you can bring your personal set to the gym and train without the hassle of waiting!

aPlusContent.title: Product Description
aPlusContent.rawText:
Product Description
Thick Foam Padding 
Premium high-density foam provides superior cushioning against heavy weights during hip thrusts and squats. The 17-inch length and 1.2 -inch thick padding distributes pressure evenly, eliminating discomfort on your hips and allowing you to focus on form. 
Ergonomic Shape 
Uniquely contoured design hugs the barbell securely while providing optimal positioning for hip thrusts and squats. The curved structure prevents rolling and maintains stability throughout your entire workout session. 
Dual Grip Straps 
Two heavy-duty Velcro straps ensure the pad stays firmly attached to any Olympic bar. Quick-release design allows easy attachment and removal while preventing any unwanted movement during intense workouts. 
2 Barbell Clamps 
Quick-release collars with single-lever locking mechanism. Tough and impact-resistant ABS material ensures plates stay secure during Olympic lifts and compound movements. 
2 Lifting Straps 
Cloth wrist straps that enhance grip strength during deadlifts and pulling exercises. Overall construction provides durability while preventing wrist strain and grip fatigue. 
2 Ankle Straps 
Professional-grade cable attachment with stainless steel D-rings and polyester padding. Secure velcro closure prevents slipping during leg extensions and kickbacks. 
3 Resistance Bands 
Polyester & latex exercise bands with anti-roll technology. Textured surface provides grip while the seamless construction prevents chafing. Ideal for mobility work and resistance training.

title: CAP Barbell Adjustable Dumbbell Weight Set | Multiple Options
breadCrumbs: Sports & Outdoors › Exercise & Fitness › Strength Training Equipment › Weights & Accessories › Dumbbells
features: Set includes – 52. 5 lbs. Total: one 17” dumbbell handle, two 1. 25-Pound plates, two 2. 5-Pound plates, eight 5-pound plates, and two star-lock collars.

Cast iron weight plates fit 1-inch standard handles and bars – plates will accommodate all standard 1-inch handles and bars. High-grade cast iron plates covered with black epoxy finish prevent rust and corrosion for long-lasting performance.
17-Inch diamond knurled chrome handle – crafted from cold rolled steel with medium-depth diamond knurling for a secure, firm and non-slip grip.
Star-lock collars with rubber O-rings – course thread star-lock collars are easy to tighten and loosen on threaded ends and helps keep weight plates securely fashioned while weightlifting.

Easy use & storage – compact, convenient, and easy to use and store. This all-in-one dumbbell set eliminates the need for multiple dumbbells in your home gym. Great for targeting Individual muscle groups or incorporating into a full body workout.
Included components: 1 dumbbell handle;2 collars;12 weight plates
Sport type: Weightlifting; Exercise & Fitness
